'''Karsems''' were the [[Currency/Legends|currency]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Radnor/Legends|Radnor]].

5,000 karsems was the equivalent of an average one-year's pay on the planet; it was also the price required to purchase a bio-isolation suit during the panic-riven bioplague crisis that struck Radnor in [[27 BBY/Legends|27 BBY]].

